<p style="user-select: auto;">This course is the fundamental for preparing students to understand and apply more vocabulary when encountering subjects related to technology and computing in their respective major. All of the topics are embedded with grammar, vocabulary and skills focus, therefore, students are highly recommended to continue to remember the rules of all grammar topics they have learned. The grammar topics students learn this semester will require them to practice speaking and writing using more complex English sentence structures and to produce technical descriptions and opinion essays. In this second semester, students should be able to comprehend all strategies needed to read longer texts in English to generate good comprehension and critical thinking.</p>
